data.description: Tucked away in the heart of Naples in this nice community with a community park and NO Association and no rental restrictions!!! The home has a new roof and solar panels that reduce the electric bill!! The A/C is newer along with a new water heater and new washing machine!! Newer updated kitchen and upgrades throughout the home!! There is plenty of extra storage inside and outside the home!! A new paver deck was recently installed in the back yard making for a beautiful and tranquil sitting area for those nice pit fire nights!! The home was recently re-piped throughout the home!! Just an 11 minute drive to Lowdermilk Beach Park!! Just minutes to grocery and shopping and restaurants!!
